    <item>
      <title>Docs: VirtueMart</title>
      <link>/docs/tools/shopping-cart-plugins/virtuemart.html</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 May 2021 08:39:05 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/tools/shopping-cart-plugins/virtuemart.html</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2 id=&#34;system-requirements&#34;&gt;System Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Having the PayU&amp;rsquo;s VirtueMart plugin downloaded and stored in an accessible location. Click &lt;a href=&#34;../../assets/plugins/plugin-joomla-virtuemart2.6.7.zip&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to download it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Having VirtueMart version 2 or higher installed. Refer to &lt;a href=&#34;https://virtuemart.net/download&#34;&gt;VirtueMart official website&lt;/a&gt; for more information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your VirtueMart website must be installed on &lt;a href=&#34;https://joomla.org/&#34;&gt;Joomla!®&lt;/a&gt; 2.5 or higher.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;install-the-plugin&#34;&gt;Install the plugin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow the next procedure to install the plugin on your website.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open the &lt;em&gt;Joomla!® Administrator Console&lt;/em&gt; and select the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extension Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; option located in the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Extension&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; menu.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../assets/VirtueMart/VirtueMart_01.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Upload Package File&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; section, click &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Browse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; and locate the &lt;em&gt;.zip&lt;/em&gt; file of the PayU plugin downloaded.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../assets/VirtueMart/VirtueMart_02.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;3&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Once the installation procedure completes, a message appears to inform that the installation was successful.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../assets/VirtueMart/VirtueMart_03.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;configure-the-plugin&#34;&gt;Configure the plugin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expand the option Shop in the &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VirtueMart&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; menu and select &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payment methods&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. Then, click &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; at the top right of the screen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../assets/VirtueMart/VirtueMart_04.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PrintScreen&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!-- ![PrintScreen](/assets/PaymentRequest/PaymentRequest_01.png) --&gt;
      </description>
    </item>
    
